WEBVTT

00:00:05.331 --> 00:00:07.048
Do you hear that?

00:00:09.777 --> 00:00:11.570
Do you know what that is?

00:00:13.050 --> 00:00:14.333
Silence.

00:00:14.780 --> 00:00:16.794
The sound of silence.

00:00:17.448 --> 00:00:20.142
Simon and Garfunkel wrote a song about it.

00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:23.311
But silence is a pretty
rare commodity these days,

00:00:23.335 --> 00:00:27.118
and we're all paying a price for it
in terms of our health --

00:00:27.142 --> 00:00:30.046
a surprisingly big price, as it turns out.